+-------------------+----------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| `pygame`_         | pygame         | Python Game Development.                                               |
+-------------------+----------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| `windows-curses`_ | windows-curses | Support for the standard curses module on Windows.                     |
+-------------------+----------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| `Pillow`_         | Pillow         | Python Imaging Library (Fork)                                          |
+-------------------+----------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------+


